#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""Run the Erdos #257 finite period-noncollapse theorem strike.

This is a bounded strike lane over the proof-audit DAG. It attacks the finite
theorem candidate

    S_F(b) = sum_{n in F} 1/(b^n - 1) = P / Q,  ord_Q(b) = lcm(F)

by deterministic finite search and denominator-order certificate extraction.
It does not call providers, attempt the infinite Erdos #257 proof, or post
upstream.
"""

